## Response Formats

### GET (database exists)
```json
{
  "dbName": "app_myproject",
  "dbUser": "app_myproject_user",
  "sizeBytes": 8421376,
  "activeConnections": 2,
  "connectionString": "postgresql://app_myproject_user:xxxx@rds-endpoint:5432/app_myproject?sslmode=require",
  "createdAt": "2026-03-01T12:00:00.000Z"
}
```

### GET (no database)
```json
null
```

### POST (success, 201)
```json
{
  "dbName": "app_myproject",
  "dbUser": "app_myproject_user",
  "connectionString": "postgresql://app_myproject_user:xxxx@rds-endpoint:5432/app_myproject?sslmode=require",
  "message": "Database created successfully. DATABASE_URL has been set for production and preview."
}
```

### POST (conflict, 409)
```json
{
  "error": "Database already exists for this project"
}
```

### DELETE (success, 200)
```json
{
  "message": "Database deleted successfully"
}
```

### DELETE (bad confirmation, 400)
```json
{
  "error": "Confirmation name does not match"
}
```

---

## Error Handling

| Error Scenario | HTTP Status | Response |
|----------------|-------------|----------|
| Invalid project UUID | 400 | `{ "error": "Invalid project ID" }` |
| Project not found | 404 | `{ "error": "Project not found" }` |
| Database already exists (POST) | 409 | `{ "error": "Database already exists for this project" }` |
| No database exists (DELETE) | 404 | `{ "error": "No database exists for this project" }` |
| Confirmation name mismatch (DELETE) | 400 | `{ "error": "Confirmation name does not match" }` |
| RDS connection failure | 500 | `{ "error": "Failed to create/delete database" }` |
| Unauthenticated | 401 | `{ "error": "Unauthorized" }` (handled by `withAuth`) |

---

## Verification

- [ ] GET returns `null` (200) for project with no database
- [ ] GET returns database info with stats for project with database
- [ ] GET returns connection string with decrypted password
- [ ] GET returns 404 for non-existent project
- [ ] POST creates database and returns 201
- [ ] POST returns 409 if database already exists
- [ ] POST sets `DATABASE_URL` env vars (verify via `GET /api/projects/:id/env?scope=production`)
- [ ] DELETE returns 200 on successful deletion
- [ ] DELETE returns 400 if `confirmName` doesn't match
- [ ] DELETE returns 404 if no database exists
- [ ] All routes return 401 for unauthenticated requests
- [ ] Invalid UUID returns 400
